sys-power/acpi-stuff 9999: Few modules for ACPI debugging
sys-power/bbswitch 9999: Toggle discrete NVIDIA Optimus graphics card
x11-misc/optidesk 9999: Tool to add .desktop files to be used by optirun
x11-misc/primus 9999: Faster OpenGL offloading for Bumblebee
x11-misc/virtualgl 9999-r3: Run OpenGL applications remotely with full 3D hardware acceleration
